 Strap in, gun your engine and go full throttle into the most turbocharged,
 hi-octane combat racing game to hit Steam. From the developers behind the
 epic Midnight Club series, Carnage Racing combines seat-of-the-pants driving,
 tricks and stunts with explosive vehicle combat in a no-holds-barred race

 Take on the rest of the world with Carnage Racing's exhilarating 8-way real

 buy upgrades that'll power you to global victory. Get ready for the race of
